{"tid":774712,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"山東青州市鎮兩級財政緊張 年利率12.5%向公務員借款","createTime":"2018-08-10T13:57:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-10T14:53:52.000Z","uid":48083,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"3b87810db1d1fcad6eb1f6afead9e5eb9e462af6","tid":774712,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T13:57:01.000Z","msg":"據財聯社報道，記者獲悉，山東青州市鎮兩級政府因為財政緊張，啓動面向機關工作人員暫借部分資金用於週轉，借款金額5萬元起步，年利率12.5%，政府代扣代繳利息個人所得稅，稅後年利率10%，借款之日起6個月後，債權人可以提取本金。籌款時間為10個工作日（2018年8月13日-24日）。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.sohu.com/a/246435904_313745/?pvid=000115_3w_a\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.sohu.com%2Fa%2F246435904_313745%2F%3Fpvid%3D000115_3w_a&d=E0p321MZ84jFeSRkm7K84fiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=186551f3\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.sohu.com/a/246435904_313745/?pvid=000115_3w_a</a>"},{"pid":"5c86afffd9d5c16370694d44edc2e31b57a0c91e","tid":774712,"uid":1643,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T13:58:47.000Z","msg":"半年提取同面值真陰司紙"},{"pid":"2d25dc44569f1bc498ab492a511180ca1a978d0a","tid":774712,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T14:01:13.000Z","msg":"8月10日，澎湃新聞（<a href=\"http://www.thepaper.cn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thepaper.cn&d=E0p321MZ84jFeSRkm7K84fiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=da55e768\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.thepaper.cn</a>）從青州市市委有關部門獲悉，上述通知是黃樓街道辦事處向青州市人民政府彙報的版本，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">屬於暫定方案，8月10日下午被青州市人民政府否定，並未實施。</span><br />\n</strong><br />\n上述通知規定，借款金額5萬元起（以1萬的整數倍增加），多者不限；年利率為12.5%，政府代扣代繳利息個人所得稅，稅後年利率為10%；自借款之日起滿6個月後，債權人需用該資金時可隨時提取本金，數額較大者提前與財政所聯繫，以保證正常提取。<br />\n<br />\n此外，借款籌備時間10個工作日（2018年8月13日-24日）；開戶行是青州農商行黃樓支行，戶名是青州市黃樓街道韓家社區服務中心，賬號是9070107054642050000764；匯款之後，本人攜帶銀行回單至財政所辦理相關手續。<br />\n<br />\n同時，該通知還聲明「詳情咨詢財政所」，注明的下發時間為2018年8月9日。<br />\n<br />\n責任編輯：劉萬里 SF014<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://finance.sina.cn/2018-08-10/detail-ihhnunsr0306060.d.html?from=wap\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.sina.cn%2F2018-08-10%2Fdetail-ihhnunsr0306060.d.html%3Ffrom%3Dwap&d=E0p321MZ84jFeSRkm7K84fiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=8b914546\" target=\"_blank\">https://finance.sina.cn/2018-08-10/detail-ihhnunsr0306060.d.html?from=wap</a><br />\n<br />\n份野係堅，不過<del>揚咗之後就</del>冇實施啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef9d957ab40e347bfac7cd54c597074cbdfb9565","tid":774712,"uid":75326,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T14:04:42.000Z","msg":"一定還得到，不過半年後唔知會唔貶值50%"},{"pid":"c5d3ec921f939a05484642d4c1ade8011d85bb16","tid":774712,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T14:15:40.000Z","msg":"即係你老細冇糧出俾你<br />\n叫你借錢俾佢出糧俾你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c33dd4ac9c381c4d3b8b41e0df2c2ddeda41acf8","tid":774712,"uid":53687,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c5d3ec921f939a05484642d4c1ade8011d85bb16","tid":774712,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T14:15:40.000Z","msg":"即係你老細冇糧出俾你<br />\n叫你借錢俾佢出糧俾你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T14:19:08.000Z","msg":"咁似亞視叫員工入股<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e131dea0079822ac6f63dfebe1bc3b7a9a85ed55","tid":774712,"uid":44454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T14:21:09.000Z","msg":"到期日同你全部股換債<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c2328735fce31cca8a6c420aa1e3547a0bfc009","tid":774712,"uid":24853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T14:21:26.000Z","msg":"支爆了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"444174454b2379f751213873925d396e1ebdef6d","tid":774712,"ui